[Student "S"]
{SOUTH cannot use RKCB at her second bid because trumps have not been agreed. So she bids 
3\H to set trumps, knowing NORTH cannot pass after her jump-shift. 

NORTH tries to stop at game but SOUTH is too strong so she now uses RKCB and gets 
to 6\H when NORTH shows two Key Cards and the trump Queen.}

